content: Keep your collection of geeky literature organized and propped up in an eye catching manner using these Star Wars AT-AT bookends. Crafted from solid wood, they’re engraved with fine detailing and are meticulously assembled by hand to ensure quality.

titleEN: Light Up League Of Legends Crystals
content: Bring your favorite champion to life by lighting up your room with one of these League Of Legends crystals. Each brilliantly cut crystal sits on an elegant base and contains an embedded LED that brings the laser engraving to life.

Show our neighboring planets some love by giving your outfit some cosmic flair with this solar system planets ring. Each ring is cast in silver and adorned with a small handmade pendant depicting all the planets in our solar system.

titleEN: Co-Workers I Want To Punch Notebook
content: Take a detour off the high road and succumb to your petty ways by keeping track of everyone who’s ever crossed you with help from this discreet notebook. It sports an elegant black buckrum cover and provides enough space to fit your growing list of enemies.

Document your life’s most memorable events in true Whovian style by writing them down in this Doctor Who TARDIS journal. This handmade journal features a sturdy cardboard cover designed to look like the Doctor’s iconic space and time traveling machine.

Turn a fun project into Junior’s favorite place to rest by crafting him a comfy hanging cloth crib. This simple DIY project shows you how to make a sturdy hammock-like crib that your infant will love rocking in all day long.

Make your cinephile buddies green with envy by bringing home this swimming Alien prop. This stunning statue is masterfully hand sculpted from a rigid rubber using incredible detailing that stretches over 12 feet long – making it the ideal centerpiece for any room.

Bring everyone’s favorite merc with a mouth to life by dressing up in this Deadpool replica motorcycle suit. Styled exactly like Deadpool’s signature ensemble, this all leather suit will protect you from road rash and give you a license to mess with anyone you want.

Have the kids set sail for fun and adventure by surprising them with this wooden ship treehouse. This elaborately themed treehouse is handmade with superb attention to detail and features 130 square feet of actual deck space.

Get your hands springtime clean by rubbing them in dog shit. This novelty dog poop shaped soap is handmade from natural ingredients that won’t harm the skin and has surprisingly pleasant fragrance despite its outward appearance.

Give your outfit a stunning a nerdy touch by accenting it with this lovely solar system planet necklace. The necklace features a vintage brass coating and comes with two sided pendants displaying our solar system’s most beautiful planets in vivid color.

Earth’s mightiest warrior has come to save you from the darkness in the form of this Goku kamehameha lamp. This handmade lamp features the legendary Saiyan hero shooting an enormous kamehameha wave that provides some ambient lighting.

Give your poker games a George R.R. Martin twist with these Game Of Thrones playing cards. Each face card of this hand illustrated deck features the series’ main characters like Robb Stark and Jon Snow and are decorated with a map of Westeros on the back.

Give any room a touch of gamer flair by bringing in this NES controller coffee table. This geeky piece of furniture is painted to look like a giant version of the classic NES controller and is covered with a protective polyurethane layer.

Give your contemporary home a bit of old world charm with this vintage light bulbs chandelier. This work of art features a multicolor salvaged wood board base along with sixty vintage bulbs hanging at various heights that combine for a stunning glow.

Get your tired body feeling like new again by dropping an achy muscles bath bomb in your bathtub. It’s made with carefully selected essential oils and natural ingredients to provide a top quality aromatherapy bathing experience.

Transform your backyard into the coolest hangout spot ever with one of these custom built treehouses. They’re expertly built from solid wood and designed around the tree’s existing structure, guaranteeing no two are alike.

Become the living embodiment of Titus by suiting up in this life size space marine costume. This custom made UVA foam suit covers you from head to toe in thick armor that’s decorated to look just like a space marine from Warhammer 40K.

Bring some style into your home office with this rustic reclaimed wood desk. Available in a variety of elegant finishes, each desk is handmade from reclaimed wood and accented with distinguished and sturdy mid century steel legs.

Drink your brew with a little old world charm by sipping if out of one these medieval oak mugs. The mugs are handcrafted from solid wood and finished off with a sturdy stainless steel handle for a secure and comfy grip while you drink.

Give your two-wheeled ride a little nighttime flair by accenting it using these LED bicycle wheel lights. Each light is made to fit most adult sized bikes and gives off a bright neon glow designed to increase your visibility with style.

Get an extra jolt of energy from your sugary treats by snaking on these coffee bean cookies. Each savory cookie comes garnished with a mix of chocolate chips and dark roast coffee beans that make this the perfect treat for coffee lovers and dessert lovers alike.

Turn yourself into a delicious sugary snack by making cookies of your beautiful mug using these custom portrait cookie cutters. After submitting your photo, you’ll be sent a 3D printed mold of your face so you can stamp it on some fresh dough.

Secure your spot as parent of the year by surprising your little hell raisers with this cabin treehouse. This mammoth hangout spot  is handmade from solid wood and accented with everything from a climbing wall, slide, and even a smoke stack chimney.

Set your mass produced laptop apart from the rest by giving it a playful touch using this spacebar space decal. The rectangular sticker is handmade from vinyl and displays four colorful planets from our solar system surrounded by a flurry of stars.

Bring an air of whimsy to any room in your home by lighting up this faerie magick candle. Sprinkled with glitter and topped with colorful dripping wax accents, the candle is designed to burn for 45 hours while release an intoxicating aroma.

Real roses are so cliché. Get your honey something she’ll actually appreciate by purchasing a lovely bouquet of these piranha plants! Inspired from the classic Super Mario Bros series – it’s sure to be the centerpiece in any room.

Step your texting game up by creating a personalized emoji of yourself. Simply submit a photo of your lovely mug and you’ll receive a custom image in both .jpg and .png format that you can then use to bombard friends and family with while texting.

Give any room in your home an extra inviting atmosphere by lighting up this cereal scented candle. This handmade soy wax candle comes with a cotton wick inside an elegant glass jar and features a delightful Cap’n Crunch aroma.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Pool Table
content: Give your man cave a futuristic feel by lighting the room up with this glow in the dark pool table. This 7 foot table can be customized with your choice of colored felt and comes outfitted with bright light strips that give the table a cool futuristic glow.

Increase your odds of making whoopee by buttering up your sweetie with one of these red velvet whoopie pies. These delectable treats are baked with all-natural organic ingredients and come filled with soft velvety cream cheese icing.

Bring your little crime fighter’s favorite comic to life by transforming their bed into a Batmobile. Using this downloadable PDF and a bit of elbow grease, you’ll be able to completely change you child’s standard twin bed into a bitchin’ Batmobile.

titleEN: Put A Ring On It Mug
content: Belittle your single friends, family, and co-workers by flaunting around your happiness using this this personalized engagement mug. The printed message will spread the joyous news while not so subtly directing the eyes to that fat rock.

Instantly spice up any plain outfit with a little color by slipping into these tie dye rainbow Converse. These classic high tops provide a comfy fit and are expertly dyed by hand, ensuring that no two pairs are the same.

Turn fantasy into reality by giving your partner this Valentine’s Day naughty coupon booklet. This downloadable PDF gives you all the tools necessary to construct a fourteen coupon booklet you and your lover can customize with all your perverted desires.

Ensure your delicate smartphone remains protected and always at hand by placing it inside this steampunk iPhone case bracer. Handmade from steel, brass, and leather, this unique case allows you to wear your phone like a piece of jewelry.

titleEN: Take Off Your Pants Valentine’s Card
content: Skip the games and romantic banter and get straight to the good stuff by giving your sweetie this “Take Off Your Pants” valentine’s card. It humorously tweaks the classic “roses are red, violets are blue” poem so your significant other knows what’s in store.

Experience first hand what out world actually looks and feels like by hanging up this scientifically accurate 3D topographic relief carving. Crafted from crack resistant kiln dried Canadian Maple, the carving displays our world’s terrain with impeccable detail.

Spark up like a true Pokemaster by sliding your trusty Bic into one of these Pokemon lighter sleeves. Each handmade hard sleeve is designed to look exactly like a classic Pokemon card that’s sure to make you the envy of all your geeky friends.

Navigate through the treacherous land of <del>Hyrule</del> suburbia using this Navi fairy replica light. Handmade from resin, each lamp features an embedded LED that can be changed to 1 of 6 vibrant colors – and it fits in the palm of your hand.

Indulge your eyes as well as your taste buds by feasting on these rainbow Rice Krispies treats. Each batch is handmade from scratch and comes professionally packaged to ensure freshness in every single bite.

Show your significant other how much they mean to you with the modern times Valentine’s Day card. Sonnets, poetry, and love songs are simply too outdated. This novelty card contains a message your sweetheart will love – and most likely will post on Instagram.

Disconnect from the modern world and get in touch with mother nature by spending a night in this treehouse tent. With running electricity, a comfy bed, and a working bathroom, this luxurious treetop abode is sure to make your night in nature unforgettable.

Bring the galaxy’s most lethal bounty hunter to your city by dressing up in this Super Metroid Varia suit. It’s expertly crafted from lightweight materials to facilitate movement – making it the ideal costume for any convention.

Skip the games and let your Valentine know how you really feel about them with these custom chocolate messages. They’re handmade from creamy milk chocolate and are skillfully decorated with any message you’d like – no matter how crude or kinky.

You smart. You very smart. We da best. You a genius. I appreciate you. You loyal.  This DJ Khaled Valentine’s card features the big buy himself with his heart in his hands so your sweetheart knows that with him/her by your side, you can always win win win no matter what.

Keep your cat from scratching up your furniture in true gamer fashion using this Pac-Man cat complex. It installs directly onto the wall to save space and features graphics designed to look like a level from the iconic arcade game.

Go from rags to riches without needing a fairy godmother by slipping into this beautiful Cinderella dress. Based on the dress from the live action movie, this gorgeous blue gown can be customized to your exact measurements for a perfect fit.

Give your game room a touch of geeky accent lighting with this unique Pac-Man LEGO lamp. Handmade entirely from LEGO bricks, each lamp comes with an embedded LED that illuminates the Pac-Man themed 8-bit graphics on each side.

Join the ranks of the ancient brotherhood by getting into this Assassin’s Creed Ezio Auditore costume. It features game accurate symbols and is made from genuine leather and fur to create an amazing life-like appearance.

Bring nature into your indoor environment with this Japanese moss ball aquarium. Each small glass sphere contains a tiny aquatic ecosystem complete with sand, a small shell, and a clump of moss – ideal for creating a relaxing atmosphere.

Live your life like a fabulous bitch by outfitting your home with this “Press For Champagne” button. This handmade piece of home decor measures 10.75 x 7.25 inches and features a lovely ornate frame that’s perfect for your blue blooded lifestyle.

Turn heads the next time you walk out of the house by wearing these shark bite spiked wedges. It’s expertly hand painted and decorated with dozens of differently sized spikes along the heels to resemble the fearsome jaw of a great white.

Give any room an eerie atmosphere using this anatomically correct human skull replica. This macabre piece of home decor is expertly crafted from plaster of Paris then skillfully painted and weathered for a realistic appearance.

Announce your pending nuptials with humor using these “Shit Just Got Real” wedding announcement cards. This folded card measures 5.5 x 4.2 inches, comes in an elegant recycled kraft envelope, and is perfect for couples that like telling it like it is.

Don’t fret if the big guy upstairs isn’t taking your calls – because these celebrity prayer candles will make all your wishes come true! Each candle displays a pop culture icon like Miley Cyrus or the phenomenal Kylie Jenner dressed up in traditional religious garments.

Now that the Force has awakened, don’t miss your opportunity to become an illustrious Jedi warrior. Each personalized Jedi Knight certificate acknowledges that you have all the training and skills necessary to wield a lightsaber.

Keep your library upright using these skateboard bookends. Made for skaters by skaters, each bookend utilizes the tail end of a real skateboard, making these these the ideal pieces to keep your books and skate magazines organized.

Display every member of your clan in a creative and unique way using this family tree wall decal. Available in two sizes ranging from 80 to 90 inches tall, the branches provide the ideal spot to hang your most treasured family pictures.

Keep your home organized in an eye-catching way by hanging these decorative jumbo clothespins on your wall. Each 12 inch long handcrafted clothespin is given a gorgeous dark walnut finish and comes with a brass plated tooth hanger in the back for easy set up.

Instantly turn yourself into a magnificent sea creature by curling up in this beautiful mermaid tail blanket. It’s hand knit from soft acrylic and comes in infant, child, and adult sizes so every member of the family can join in on the fun.

Stand out from your fellow collectors by incorporating this authentic gold plated Buffalo nickel into your coin collection. Introduced in 1913, the Buffalo nickel comes coated in 24 karat gold and is considered by many to be a token of good luck.

Keep friends and family from ruining your clean carpet with their filthy shoes with a blunt message from this “Shoes Off, Bitches” doormat. This waterproof mat is made from a sturdy synthetic fiber that makes it ideal for indoor or outdoor use.

Decorate your home with some striking beauty using these glass blown spiders. Each arachnid is hand-blown with impeccable detail, measures around 2 inches long, and is decorated in a blend of vivid and varied colors.

Give yourself an out of this world look by accessorizing with this lovely moon pendant necklace. The tiny full moon is encased in a glass dome and attached to an elegant antique brass necklace that you can sport at both casual and formal events.

Cats and the ’80s – what’s not to love? The world’s most amazing cat calendar displays a grumpy black cat in twelve different and totally rad ’80s themed photos dressed up as icons like Rob Ross, Pee Wee Herman, and the gents from Miami Vice.

Break away from all the angles and straight edges in your home decor with this handcrafted tile mosaic coffee table. This circular table has a 38 inch diameter and displays a striking tile design at the center that adds depth and character to the piece.

Beep boop beep bop – these R2-D2 LED pumps are definitely the party shoes you’ve been searching for. They’re painted by hand, customized with cool droid-like accents and contain embedded LED modules that cycle between 8 vibrant color combinations.

Show off your geeky side by accenting your look with this big dipper silver earring. The earring requires only one pierced ear and is cast in sterling silver in the familiar shape of one of the night sky’s most recognized constellations.

Easily give any room a little more character using this singular octopus lamp. Handcrafted from resin, brass and silver, this fun nautical lamp stands over eight inches tall and utilizes the octopus’s tentacles as a sturdy base.

Pizza is everyone’s favorite food – and now with this catnip pizza toy it can be your kitty’s favorite too. This six inch pizza is handmade from soft cotton fabric and cut into four small slices each filled with all natural organic catnip.

Make a room go from plain to quaint without spending a fortune with this wooden candle holder. This rustic lighting device is fitted to hold 5 small candles and is handmade from salvaged wood like Black Cherry, Walnut, Elm, and Maple.

Violently blow your diet away by scarfing down this life size chocolate gun. Handmade from rich milk chocolate in the good ol’ gun-loving U.S. of A., this non-lethal treat sports incredibly realistic detailing and comes in an actual padded gun case.

Handle arts and crafts like a true Pokemaster by constructing one of these incredible Pokemon paper masks. This downloadable PDF provides step by step instructions on how to end up with a cool looking mask using only basic materials.

Give your baked goodies some stunning visual appeal by baking them with this engraved maze rolling pin. Handmade from beech wood, the pin comes etched with an intricate maze-like pattern so your treats have some added texture and appeal.

Recreate the majesty of our planetary neighbors in stunning detail using these solar system cross stitch patterns. These downloadable patterns  will guide you step by step so you can create visually stunning and detailed renditions of planets like Mars and Jupiter.

Set off an explosion of flavor in your mouth by sinking your teeth into one of these chocolate hand grenades. Made with rich Belgian chocolate, it’s crafted from an life size replica mills explosive and packed with mouthwatering chocolate covered beans.

Add a touch of magic to family game night by playing everyone’s favorite board game with these Harry Potter Monopoly pieces. They’re handmade from polymer clay and come in various fun designs like Harry’s broom, the sorting hat, and chocolate frogs.

There’s no better remedy for chapped lips than unicorn poop. In addition to the enchanted fecal matter, this handmade balm incorporates natural ingredients like cocoa butter, shea butter, and beeswax for unmatched moisture.

Add a splash of color to your outfit using these tie up gladiator sandals. These handmade Greek leather sandals sport the classic gladiator tie up style and come decorated with vibrant pom poms, semi-precious stones and friendship bracelets sown into the shoe.

Gain a new appreciation for the cosmos by experiencing its incredible taste with these galaxy lollipops. Available in sets of six, each lollipop features a breathtaking image of our universe and comes with a sweet cotton candy flavor.

Create an intimate and romantic nighttime atmosphere in your home by illuminating the room with this candle light chandelier. Handcrafted from wood, it’s thirty inches at its widest point and designed to hold up to sixteen small candles.

Always ripe and ready to eat – these cantaloupe panties will make your hoo-ha look that much more appetizing. These unmentionables are made from ultra soft organic cotton and come with a pink stretch lace border for a snug fit.

Entertain your kids for hours by filling their heads with wonder with the Brothers Grim story book. The custom made book combines the classic stories like Sleeping Beauty and Cinderella combined with select images taken from the Once Upon A Time TV series.

Give your outfit a hippie chic vibe by toting your stuff around in this Volkswagen Bus purse. Made from genuine leather, the exterior is styled to look like a miniature version of the iconic VW Bus and comes with two zippered pockets.

Maintain your sanity on a stressful day by melting your cares away with this “Calm Your Tits” scented candle. Ideal for use in aromatherapy, the candle contains a soothing blend of chamomile, mandarin, lavender, and lily of the valley.

Bring your favorite video game character to life by transforming yourself with these League of Legends Vi fists. They’re handmade from EVA foam and skillfully painted to achieve the highest level of realism, making them ideal for cosplay.

titleEN: Star Wars Kylo Ren LIghtsaber Hilt
content: Become the First Order’s top warrior by channeling the power of the Dark Side with this Kylo Ren lightsaber hilt. This 3D printed collectible is made from durable ABS plastic and is skillfully decorated to look like Kylo Ren’s unique lightsaber.

Take friends and family with you wherever you go by carrying around these personalized fabric dolls. Their outfits can be customized to your liking and the dolls come with just enough detail to work sufficiently as voodoo dolls.

Detonate an explosion of flavor in your mouth by biting into one of these chocolate grenades. Made entirely from rich milk chocolate, each full sized grenade is sealed in a plastic bag and then placed inside a novelty “explosives” tin to ensure freshness.

Class up your phone’s look without spending a bundle by slipping it into this black marble iPhone case. Made from plastic and acrylic, it’s designed to shield your phone from minor scratches and features a stylish design that wraps around the entire case.

Receive a world class back massage while your kids play by slipping into this wearable playmat shirt. While you lay comfortably on your stomach, the kids are kept entertained as they roll their jagged plastic toy cars across the streets printed on the back of the shirt.

Show off your adventurous side without permanently marking your body using this world map temporary tattoo. It goes on easily, comes off with soap water, and is small enough to place virtually anywhere on your body.

Create an inviting atmosphere in your home by releasing the intoxicating aroma of this unicorn farts scented candle. This hand poured candle is made from all natural wax and is highly scented with a sweet and tangy aroma of vanilla, strawberry, kiwi, and coconut.

Fight off the cold by wrapping yourself up in one of these chunky yarn scarf shawls. Available in a variety of hues like mocha and charcoal, this garment is hand crocheted from acrylic yarn and can be worn in different forms to suit your style.

Experience a spa quality cleansing from the comfort of home by scrubbing yourself clean with these luxury soaps for men. These vegan-approved soaps combines all natural oils and butters to provide a deep cleanse that absorbs dirt with ease.

Celebrate the joys and pitfalls of coffee by pouring a hot roast into this humorous mug. This 11 ounce mug is made from quality ceramic and uses a process where the ink is infused into the mug so the funny caption will never fade.

You don’t need to be a hardcore garden enthusiast to enjoy this functional gag gift. Perfect for any adult with a sense of humor and a green thumb, this clever kit allows you to grow your new pair of balls into delicious basil and oregano plants!

Brighten up your outfit by adding some color to it with these rainbow Converse shoes. These classic high tops provide a superbly comfy fit and come decked out in a blend of bright colors ranging from yellow to turquoise and orange.

Create an alluring look by styling your hair like a fashionable mermaid with this pastel blue hair dye. The dye is highly pigmented so it lasts longer and features a pleasant scent infused with Moroccan Argan oils, camellia, and other conditioners.
